OL,3,CDVLA: Lengthy waits for drivers with
OL,4,Cmedical conditions to renew licenses
OL,6,FOlder drivers in Wales say lengthy
OL,7,Fdelays in renewing their driving
OL,8,Flicences are leaving them anxious,
OL,9,Ffrustrated and, in some cases,
OL,10,Freluctant to get behind the wheel.
OL,12,FWhile the Driver and Vehicle Licensing
OL,13,FAgency (DVLA) says many
OL,14,Fstraightforward licence renewals can
OL,15,Fbe completed within days, new figures
OL,16,Fobtained by ITV Wales through a
OL,17,FFreedom of Information (FOI) request
OL,18,Freveal that applications requiring
OL,19,Fmedical assessments are taking
OL,20,Fsignificantly longer than the agency's
OL,21,Fown target.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
