OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1781039474
OL,3,CDVLA: Lengthy waits for drivers with
OL,4,Cmedical conditions to renew licenses
OL,6,FThe uncertainty is affecting daily
OL,7,Flife and holiday plans for pensioners.
OL,9,FFor 82-year-old Glenda Edwards,
OL,10,Fdriving has long been an important
OL,11,Fpart of maintaining her independence.
OL,13,FIn January, she applied to renew her
OL,14,Fdriving licence, a process that is
OL,15,Frequired by all drivers over the age
OL,16,Fof 70 every three years. As part of
OL,17,Fthe application, she declared that she
OL,18,Fhad glaucoma.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1781039474
OL,3,CDVLA: Lengthy waits for drivers with
OL,4,Cmedical conditions to renew licenses
OL,6,FHowever, Glenda says she has since
OL,7,Fbeen informed by her doctor that she
OL,8,Fdoes not have the condition. Despite
OL,9,Frepeated attempts to update the DVLA,
OL,10,Fshe says she has struggled to get
OL,11,Fthrough to anyone who can help.
OL,13,F"Sometimes they'll say there's a long
OL,14,Fqueue, try again later," she said.
OL,16,F"Other times they'll say you can hold
OL,17,Fon and we'll call you back. You press
OL,18,Fthe buttons and they never, ever ring
OL,19,Fback."
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@XO]xD@AOU{D@FO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1781039474
OL,3,CDVLA: Lengthy waits for drivers with
OL,4,Cmedical conditions to renew licenses
OL,6,FThe months-long wait has taken a toll
OL,7,Fon her confidence.
OL,9,F"I don't want to go anywhere unless I
OL,10,Fhave to. I don't use the car as much
OL,11,Fas I used to," she said.
OL,13,FAsked whether that had been because of
OL,14,Fthe licence situation, she replied:
OL,15,F"Yes. It's had a devastating impact on
OL,16,Fme."
OL,18,FConcerned by her well-being, Glenda
OL,19,Fasked a friend to help her navigate
OL,20,Fthe process.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@NO]wD@AOUxD@DO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1781039474
OL,3,CDVLA: Lengthy waits for drivers with
OL,4,Cmedical conditions to renew licenses
OL,6,F"When I turned up to have this chat
OL,7,Fonline she was in tears," her friend
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"She's been very distressed by it.
OL,11,FMore so because she doesn't have her
OL,12,Flicence and she's worried about being
OL,13,Fstopped by the police. She's worried
OL,14,Fwhether she should be driving or not.
OL,15,FIt's had a huge, huge impact on her."
OL,17,FAnd Glenda's experience is not unique.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@YO]rD@AOUwD@eO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/14
