OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1781039474
OL,3,CDVLA: Lengthy waits for drivers with
OL,4,Cmedical conditions to renew licenses
OL,6,FByron Jenkins told ITV Cymru Wales
OL,7,Fthat his wife, who applied to renew
OL,8,Fher licence in November, had waited
OL,9,Fmore than six months for a decision.
OL,11,FWondering whether others were
OL,12,Fexperiencing similar problems, he
OL,13,Fposted in a local Facebook group.
OL,15,F"I was surprised," he said.
OL,17,F"Within an hour I had 28 replies. At
OL,18,Fleast a dozen of them were telling a
OL,19,Fsimilar story and it all seemed to do
OL,20,Fwith health information."
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@RO]yD@AOU|D@YO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1781039474
OL,3,CDVLA: Lengthy waits for drivers with
OL,4,Cmedical conditions to renew licenses
OL,6,FSome told him they had waited more
OL,7,Fthan 10 months for a decision.
OL,9,FWhile Byron accepts that medical
OL,10,Fchecks are important for road safety,
OL,11,Fhe believes prolonged delays may
OL,12,Fcreate unintended consequences.
OL,14,F"They want to ensure people are safe
OL,15,Fto drive and I understand that," he
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,F"But by taking as long as they are,
OL,19,Fthey are being counterproductive and
OL,20,Fthey are causing maybe the roads not
OL,21,Fto be as safe as they should be."
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@`O]zD@AOU}D@aO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
