CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1781039474
OL,3,CDVLA: Lengthy waits for drivers with
OL,4,Cmedical conditions to renew licenses
OL,6,FFollowing complaints from drivers, ITV
OL,7,FWales submitted a FOI request to the
OL,8,FDVLA seeking information about
OL,9,Fprocessing times.
OL,11,FThe response revealed that during the
OL,12,F2025/26 financial year, the average
OL,13,Ftime taken to make a licensing
OL,14,Fdecision in cases requiring
OL,15,Finvestigation of a medical condition
OL,16,Fwas 56.66 working days.
OL,18,FThat equates to more than 11 weeks.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1781039474
OL,3,CDVLA: Lengthy waits for drivers with
OL,4,Cmedical conditions to renew licenses
OL,6,FThe figure is substantially higher
OL,7,Fthan the DVLA's published target for
OL,8,Fmedical licensing applications, which
OL,9,Fstates that the agency aims to process
OL,10,Fapplications within 35 working days
OL,11,Fwhen it has all the information it
OL,12,Fneeds.
OL,14,FThe FOI response therefore suggests
OL,15,Fthe average medical case is taking
OL,16,Faround five weeks longer than the
OL,17,Fstated target.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1781039474
OL,3,CDVLA: Lengthy waits for drivers with
OL,4,Cmedical conditions to renew licenses
OL,6,FBy contrast, the DVLA processed more
OL,7,Fthan 5.18 million non-medical driving
OL,8,Flicence renewal applications during
OL,9,Fthe same financial year.
OL,11,FOf those, more than 5.15 million were
OL,12,Fcompleted within the agency's target
OL,13,Ftimescales of three working days for
OL,14,Fonline applications and 10 working
OL,15,Fdays for postal applications.
OL,17,FOne source of confusion among many
OL,18,Folder drivers is whether they are
OL,19,Flegally allowed to continue driving
OL,20,Fwhile awaiting a licence renewal
OL,21,Fdecision.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1781039474
OL,3,CDVLA: Lengthy waits for drivers with
OL,4,Cmedical conditions to renew licenses
OL,6,FSection 88 of The Road Traffic Act,
OL,7,Fallows some motorists to continue
OL,8,Fdriving provided they have applied for
OL,9,Frenewal, continue to meet the relevant
OL,10,Fmedical standards and have not been
OL,11,Ftold by a doctor or the DVLA that they
OL,12,Fshould stop driving.
OL,14,FHowever, campaigners and affected
OL,15,Fdrivers say that while the law may
OL,16,Fpermit them to continue driving, the
OL,17,Funcertainty surrounding their
OL,18,Fapplication can still create
OL,19,Fsignificant anxiety.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1781039474
OL,3,CDVLA: Lengthy waits for drivers with
OL,4,Cmedical conditions to renew licenses
OL,6,FResponding to ITV Wales' findings, the
OL,7,FDVLA apologised to customers who have
OL,8,Fexperienced lengthy waits.
OL,10,FA spokesperson said: "We are sorry for
OL,11,Fthe delays some customers have
OL,12,Fexperienced. We are currently seeing
OL,13,Fexceptionally high demand for
OL,14,Fapplications from customers with
OL,15,Fmedical conditions, which has
OL,16,Fregrettably impacted some processing
OL,17,Ftimes.
OL,19,F"When we have the information we need,
OL,20,Fwe always aim to make a decision as
OL,21,Fquickly as possible.
OL,26,@rD@VOU{D@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1781039474
OL,3,CDVLA: Lengthy waits for drivers with
OL,4,Cmedical conditions to renew licenses
OL,6,F"Our staff are working hard to reduce
OL,7,Fdelays, and we have introduced a new
OL,8,Fcasework system which is expected to
OL,9,Fdeliver significant improvements as
OL,10,Fmore customers transact via our new
OL,11,Fonline system."
OL,13,FThe agency stressed that medical
OL,14,Fassessments play a vital role in
OL,15,Fprotecting road safety and said more
OL,16,Fcomplex applications often require
OL,17,Fdetailed information from healthcare
OL,18,Fprofessionals before a decision can be
OL,19,Fmade.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@OO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
