OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1781039474
OL,3,CDVLA: Lengthy waits for drivers with
OL,4,Cmedical conditions to renew licenses
OL,6,FIt added that straightforward
OL,7,Fapplications submitted online can
OL,8,Foften be processed within a matter of
OL,9,Fdays.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/14
